---
---

<!-- Team collab banner -->
<section class="collab-banner">
  <div class="collab-text">
    <h2>Tu equipo de diseño web<br />siempre disponible por WhatsApp</h2>
    <p>Sin tickets de soporte. Sin esperar días. Respondemos en horas y resolvemos de verdad.</p>
    <div class="collab-btns">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/34600000000"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn-white"
      >💬 Escríbenos ahora</a>
      <a href="#planes" class="btn-ghost">Ver planes →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="collab-img">
    <img src="/images/team-collab.webp" alt="Colaboración en equipo" />
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Workspace hero banner -->
<div class="workspace-banner">
  <img src="/images/workspace.webp" alt="Espacio de trabajo creativo" class="workspace-img" />
  <div class="workspace-overlay">
    <div class="section-label" style="color:#A78BF5;">Nuestro estudio</div>
    <h2>Diseño con propósito,<br />código con cariño</h2>
    <p>Cada web que hacemos es un proyecto en el que creemos. Tu éxito es el nuestro.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
/* ── COLLAB BANNER ── */
.collab-banner {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, #4B2EB5 100%);
  color: white;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 40px;
  padding: 56px 7%;
}

.collab-text h2 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.collab-text p { margin-top: 12px; opacity: 0.75; font-size: 1rem; }

.collab-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px; }

.btn-white {
  background: white;
  color: var(--purple);
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.btn-white:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

.btn-ghost {
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  color: white;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.btn-ghost:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }

.collab-img { max-width: 280px; }
.collab-img img { width: 100%; }

/* ── WORKSPACE BANNER ── */
.workspace-banner { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: #eeeadc; }
.workspace-img { width: 100%; height: 380px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
.workspace-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(26,16,48,0.85) 30%, transparent 70%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0 7%;
}
.workspace-overlay h2 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  color: white;
  line-height: 1.2;
  max-width: 420px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}
.workspace-overlay p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 360px; line-height: 1.65; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .collab-banner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
  .collab-btns   { justify-content: center; }
  .collab-img    { display: none; }
}
</style>
